</em>(Grand Central Publishing)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Country music was born to tell stories and so was Jeff Zentner.Â <i>Colton Gentry&#8217;s Third Act</i> is fueled by a broken heart, and a determination to heal through hard work, forgiveness, and gritâ€”just like the very best country songs. Keep this one on repeat.&#8221;<br />
