<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://images-us.bookshop.org/ingram/9780807013625.jpg?height=500&amp;v=v2-a1af4c67b4e43d0363784e1ee5881b76" alt="Asian American Is Not a Color: Conversations on Race, Affirmative Action, and Family - Poon, Oiyan A." width="200" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Oiyan A. Poon, </strong><strong><em><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780807013625" class="external" target="_blank">Asian American Is Not a Color: Conversations on Race, Affirmative Action, and Family</a><br />
