<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Erik Larson,Â <em><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780385348744" class="external" target="_blank">The Demon of Unrest: A Saga of Hubris, Heartbreak, and Heroism at the Dawn of the Civil War</a><br />
